###

### ===== COLOR ATTRIBUTE VALUES =====

### Create Color Value 1 - Black
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "attributeId": "{{colorAttributeId}}",
  "value": "Black",
  "displayOrder": 1,
  "isActive": true
}

