### ===== QUERY OPERATIONS =====

### Get All Attribute Values
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attribute Values by Attribute ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attributes/{{colorAttributeId}}/values
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Attribute Value by ID
@attributeValueId = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values/{{attributeValueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Attribute Value
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values/{{attributeValueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "Midnight Black",
  "displayOrder": 10
}

### Delete Attribute Value
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/attribute-values/{{attributeValueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
